    "c) Security is also a significant concern.",
    "Some LFMs have been documented to generate hate speech [398], leading to offensive and psychologically harmful content and, in extreme cases, inciting violence.",
    "This is very dangerous for the users of HFM and become a potentially destabilizing factor in society.",
